This product includes software and data derived from Summoner's War Exporter
("sw-exporter") by Xzandro and contributors, licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0:

    https://github.com/Xzandro/sw-exporter

Specifically:
  * The game data tables in `src-tauri/mapping.json` are derived from that
    project's `app/mapping.js`.
  * The protocol and mapping behaviour reimplemented in `src-tauri/src/`
    (decode, proxy capture rules, monster/rune helpers) is derived from that
    project's `app/proxy/` and `app/mapping.js` modules.

The AES decryption key is NOT included in this project. It is the property of the
game's publisher and must be supplied by the end user from their own installation.
